snippet.description:

Our favorite attraction was the big red jump slide but we tried most of the other stuff as well, including the volcano.

Great fun as always, but as this was our second playground on the same day, we didn't stay that long as we were rather tired and wanted to check in to our hotel.

Indoor playground family fun for kids.

snippet.description:
This was our fourth and final playground from our recent family roadtrip. This time we play at Leo's Lekland in Jönköping, Sweden.

We've been here several times before and we really like that the playground is so big. There are lots of different attractions to play with. The only real downside is that it is a very popular place and often quite crowded.
